 high-resolution 3D mapping without external computing infrastructure or devices, and it&rsquo;s intuitive to be integrated to any existing robot platforms. The uniqueness of our colored data output pair with the AI-enhanced texture classification algorithms makes it easy to inspect the surface defect and corrosion autonomously.</span></p><hr style="page-break-before:always;display:none;"><!-- <div class="six columns">
